name: EWO Rush Chainlink Fall 2021
description:
Game controls
Use left and right arrows to move player left and right on the track and dodge obstacles. Up arrow to jump over blue barriers and down to slide under red barriers. 

Wallet Connect and Tokens
Connect your wallet to the Rinkeby Test Network to play. You will need to faucet ETH and get EWO from our team. Send your Account address to adittami@gmail.com to be sent EWO.

Once you have received EWO, Import the tokens from your Assets tab to see them in your account.

Token Contract Address: 0xC3ef707460f56d16c0c158C56a777EaD13Fa31c0

Token Symbol: EWO

Please use comments for support or contact adittami@gmail.com

Additional info
This project was submitted to the Chainlink Fall Hackathon 2021. Visit our Devpost page to learn more.
